y":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:00:21.000Z","msg":"地盤都難啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f918a1e69f115fa5cf3d7557d01bdcaeaf5a8228","tid":81252,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:04:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>機械人？幾錢個呀，又要請人維修fix bug, 有問題又要搵人頂，真係普及到先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本係人工高嘅地方先有潛力<br />\n香港請個廢老平平地，又唔洗請it狗</blockquote><br />\n有一日去美心MX自助機jam左紙，咪又係廢老c9開殼，清jam紙，refund，使鬼IT狗！<br />\n<br />\n（第日去睇，2部機都暫停使用）"},{"pid":"46e048c6b392e6fe94cfe69739cdee2f9a0d9dd2","tid":81252,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:05:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>M記都用機唔用人落order<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第時可能有埋機自動執餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394aadb21d65d57a7192f2f1dfc6efc22c9d81b0","tid":81252,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:31:57.000Z","msg":"最驚應該係日本人<br />\n佢地d自動化真係好前衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a044574657d07fd5558890b56002daf1271b3a9","tid":81252,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:41:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最驚應該係日本人<br />\n佢地d自動化真係好前衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大把日本人思想好守舊<br />\n仲用緊PDA 傳真機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99b5c4fba60e237f7f79d59fa443fc36d382127","tid":81252,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T17:48:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最驚應該係日本人<br />\n佢地d自動化真係好前衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大把日本人思想好守舊<br />\n仲用緊PDA 傳真機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真正驚應該係歐美國家<br />\n嗰啲國家人工高，效率低，搵部機做仲化算<br />\n而且嗰邊啲人已經好興乜柒都玩電子，所以呢家嘢普及得特別快<br />\n<br />\n譬如英國啲超市咁，30個收銀櫃台可能講緊25部係機，淨番5部人手用嚟照顧廢老同豪客，頂多請兩條蛋散企喺部機側邊處理下雜症，派下膠袋咁<br />\n<br />\n香港唔同講法喇，人工低，文化環境迫成下做嘢快，所以一部機成本可能夠請幾個。咁自然就無乜意欲玩機住啦"},{"pid":"fb63ebdc174e344321c0fbc3e6bdd1b191514344","tid":81252,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T17:57:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVmzYz8a1QGNRrHRVnSGxLDYURoH4NgtCyLMSs3E1zo34?filename=78t796L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F78t796L.jpg&h=573d47f2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b993f696acf32575d09646ab5dfe3f77153339","tid":81252,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:17:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"785e2ed0132dafc70af29737423f6514e13ac46f","tid":81252,"uid":46910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:27:41.000Z","msg":"有奴隸有香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7482529c14c6fbd6c46a371e19198a41a8e6ac","tid":81252,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T09:30:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最驚應該係日本人<br />\n佢地d自動化真係好前衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大把日本人思想好守舊<br />\n仲用緊PDA 傳真機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真正驚應該係歐美國家<br />\n嗰啲國家人工高，效率低，搵部機做仲化算<br />\n而且嗰邊啲人已經好興乜柒都玩電子，所以呢家嘢普及得特別快<br />\n<br />\n譬如英國啲超市咁，30個收銀櫃台可能講緊25部係機，淨番5部人手用嚟照顧廢老同豪客，頂多請兩條蛋散企喺部機側邊處理下雜症，派下膠袋咁<br />\n<br />\n香港唔同講法喇，人工低，文化環境迫成下做嘢快，所以一部機成本可能夠請幾個。咁自然就無乜意欲玩機住啦</blockquote><br />\n港豬十人用一部機就得，低成本高效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50693687d7ccd4c89f14e29879d0f73280781413","tid":81252,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T10:43:23.000Z","msg":"你諗多左喇 一日有班食古不化的老屎忽在度 香港都唔會有咁的一日IT狗都係做返IT狗喇"},{"pid":"77ac15382683edbeb6aa27b43ee6658b671577d6","tid":81252,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T10:52:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港主力炒樓，有冇機械人有乜關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支那人驚d掛<br />\n又美國撤資<br />\n又alphago咁勁"}]}